ead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3ccb9b5ded485ca6bba7c693a7bed716439336","tid":2486564,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c58749083f788f1dfb0c4f1168b598768ecda076","tid":2486564,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:00:14.000Z","msg":"巴打就巴打啦<br />\n老乜撚野師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:16:25.000Z","msg":"巴咩打"},{"pid":"d3dd9eac3cdc8c754a6a214e1e599c1c5dcc2797","tid":2486564,"uid":10876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"47a3bc08ee59bf0b66846078f51f5159353ab2d1","tid":2486564,"uid":117837,"like":77,"dislike":1,"score":76,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:32:22.000Z","msg":"陶傑：亂叫老師<br />\n<br />\n不知何時起，大陸民間時興把看似有幾分學問的中老年男子，不論親疏，都叫「老師」。<br />\n<br />\n余秋雨叫余老師，易中天叫易老師。就是艾未未，沒敢叫，大佬呀，清末民國，叫得老師，是要有正式的拜師儀式的：敬一盞茶，用紅盤子，盛一把間尺，恭敬奉上，禮成之後，做學生的還要掏腰包擺一桌拜師宴。<br />\n<br />\n「天地君親師」，做老師，是很嚴肅的名份，「一日為師，終身為父」，稱一個人做老師，要跟叫一個人做爸爸一樣慎重。你會在街上隨便叫一個戴眼鏡而面有鬍子的男人做爸爸嗎？<br />\n<br />\n但大陸上見一個似有點學識的人，即男簇女擁，好似花果山上的眾小猴拉着回家的齊天大聖般叫「老師」。眾小猴叫孫悟空做爺爺，是真的有名份，「老師」沒有。<br />\n<br />\n香港的一些學者和自命的知識份子，飄飄然的很享受北上大陸時被稱「老師」的感覺，他們覺得在香港特區，中環AO、食環官僚、商場師奶，只識崇拜謝霆鋒，從來不把「讀書人」當人，一過羅湖橋，難得老師前老師後的一片熱衷，很多愛國愛民的特區文人，流下了熱淚。<br />\n<br />\n小心呀，一翻臉，學生也可以鬥爭老師的，文革的宋要武，不是把老師活活打死了麼。<br />\n<br />\n陶傑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T15:14:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你會在街上隨便叫一個戴眼鏡而面有鬍子的男人做爸爸嗎？</blockquote><br />\n諗到組爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb9b95aaf587f94798615eccdbd2f0750cdce95f","tid":2486564,"uid":57868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T19:25:03.000Z","msg":"腥些"},{"pid":"a294a2d3cdec6d8531c565f84c6d6f07d66ea09c","tid":2486564,"uid":260012,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T19:38:31.000Z","msg":"有人叫摩連奴做老豆添啦<br />\n稱呼之嘛 <br />\n陶傑篇野 更加係矯枉過正<br />\n以前離婚要七出之條<br />\n呢家唔岩就離得啦<br />\n你鐘意嘅叫李榮浩柒頭又得<br />\n王祖藍柒頭都得架<br />\n一個有禮貌 D 一個冇禮貌D<br />\n你都可以叫林鄭做林師奶架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1318d2d473824b06d274e2a1c04fed01cb5df0","tid":2486564,"uid":310825,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0b08091518020017bcb598f6fedd9b75b65d0a82","tid":2486564,"uid":122134,"like":169,"dislike":0,"score":169,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:30:52.000Z","msg":"無抗拒<br />\n佢拍戲拍得好 又親身上陣<br />\n又靚仔, 我都係照叫湯告老師"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T19:58:13.000Z","msg":"Pin this plz<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb75168d37072d2e307e09a2437a38abbf75b174","tid":2486564,"uid":313237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T20:00:11.000Z","msg":"老師師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f7ab8e8d4eae4e821e0eba45bc05594f51918c","tid":2486564,"uid":356010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T20:04:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">屌你老師啦<br />\n我係唔撚叫呀，點撚樣<br />\n傻閪教畜，畜生明唔明？？</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"707f3fa43442ff2080a5c9be95744942371eb056","tid":2486564,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09f7ab8e8d4eae4e821e0eba45bc05594f51918c","tid":2486564,"uid":356010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T20:04:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">屌你老師啦<br />\n我係唔撚叫呀，點撚樣<br />\n傻閪教畜，畜生明唔明？？</spa